trans-unit.source: Represents an area within a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel"></xref> control that represents a hyperlink within the control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et område i en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel"> </xref> kontrollen som representerer en hyperkobling i kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: There are two ways to add a hyperlink to the text of a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> control.
trans-unit.target: Det er to måter å legge til en hyperkobling i teksten i en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>

trans-unit.source: You can access the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A> method of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection> class through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.Links%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> to add multiple hyperlinks to the control's text.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A>metoden for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>klasse via den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.Links%2A>for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>å legge til flere hyperkoblinger kontrollens tekst.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.Links%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you only need to add a single hyperlink to the text of the control, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkArea%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du trenger bare å legge til en hyperkobling i teksten for kontrollen, kan du bruke <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkArea%2A>for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkArea%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property accepts a LinkArea that defines the location of the hyperlink within the control's text.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen godtar LinkArea som definerer plasseringen av hyperkoblingen i kontrollens teksten.

trans-unit.source: When a hyperlink is specified using the LinkArea property, the link area is then added to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection> in the same manner as adding the link using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A> method of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Når en hyperkobling angis ved hjelp av LinkArea-egenskapen, legges deretter koblingsområdet <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>på samme måte som legger til koblingen ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A>metoden for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection.Add%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.LinkCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A> property specifies the number of characters within the text of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> to include in the link area.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>egenskapen angir antallet tegn i teksten i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>til koblingen-område.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property specifies the first character in the control text to include in the hyperlink.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>egenskapen angir det første tegnet i kontrollen teksten som skal inkluderes i hyperlink.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you want to determine whether a specific LinkArea is empty, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.IsEmpty%2A> property instead of checking the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil finne ut om en bestemt LinkArea er tom, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.IsEmpty%2A>egenskapen i stedet for kontroll av verdiene i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.IsEmpty%2A>

trans-unit.target: Nullbasert Startposisjonen for koblingsområdet i teksten i den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The number of characters, after the starting character, to include in the link area.
trans-unit.target: Antallet tegn etter det første tegnet til koblingen-område.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea"></xref> is empty.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea"> </xref> er tom.

trans-unit.source: You can use this property to determine whether a valid link area has been specified in this object instead of evaluating the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke denne egenskapen til å finne ut om et gyldig kobling-område er angitt i dette objektet i stedet for evaluering av verdiene i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the specified start and length return an empty link area; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis angitt start- og lengde returneres en tom koblingsområdet. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of characters in the link area.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir antallet tegn i koblingsområdet.

trans-unit.source: To specify text from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> to display as a link, set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property to the location in the text to start creating the link.
trans-unit.target: Angi tekst fra den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>for å vise som en kobling, kan du angi den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>egenskapen plasseringen i teksten for å begynne å opprette koblingen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>

trans-unit.source: After the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property is set, set the value of the Length property to the number of characters, including the character position specified in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property, that you want to make the link text.
trans-unit.target: Etter den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>er satt, setter du verdien til egenskapen lengde til hvor mange tegn, inkludert tegnposisjonen som er angitt i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>egenskapen som du vil opprette koblingen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you want to make the first word of the text "The quick brown fox" a link, you set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A> property to zero (0) and the Length property to three (3).
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis du vil gjøre det første ordet i teksten "God stil" en kobling, du angi den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>egenskapen til null (0) og egenskapen lengde til tre (3).</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: The number of characters, including spaces, in the link area.
trans-unit.target: Antall tegn, inkludert mellomrom, i koblingsområdet.

trans-unit.source: To specify text from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel> to display as a link, set the Start property to the location in the text to start creating the link.
trans-unit.target: Angi tekst fra den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>for å vise som en kobling, egenskapen Start til plasseringen i teksten for å begynne å opprette koblingen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel>

trans-unit.source: After the Start property is set, set the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A> property to the number of characters, including the character position specified in the Start property, that you want to make the link text.
trans-unit.target: Når Start-egenskapen er angitt, kan du angi verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>egenskapen hvor mange tegn, inkludert tegnposisjonen som er angitt i egenskapen Start som du vil gjøre koblingen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you want to make the first word of the text "The quick brown fox" a link, you set the Start property to zero (0) and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A> property to three (3).
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis du vil gjøre det første ordet i teksten "God stil" en kobling du angi Start-egenskapen til null (0) og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>egenskapen tre (3).</xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkArea.Length%2A>
